    .container
      .row.col-xs-12
        h2.pull-right About Me
      div.row.about-me.col-xs-12#about_me
        div.col-md-6
          img.profile_image(src="assets/profile_photo.png")
        div.col-md-6
          p.paragraph I'm a apprentice web developer at the Nashville Software School, a bootcamp-style vocational school focused on training junior developers. I'm new to Nashville, coming by way of Madison, WI and Birminghan, AL. When I'm not working on development projects, you can find me on the disc golf course or playing a board game with friends.

      .row.col-xs-12
        hr
        h2.pull-left Bit Blaster
      .row.col-xs-12#bit_blaster
        .col-md-6
          p.paragraph Bit Blaster is an arcade-style space shooter built with the Phaser.js game engine. I completed Bit Blaster in around two weeks while studying at Nashville Software School. I created the game assets with GIMP, and high scores are recorded using Firebase. 
            a(href="https://bitblaster.firebaseapp.com/") Play the game.
        .col-md-6
          div
            a(href="https://bitblaster.firebaseapp.com/")
              img.bit-blaster.pull-right(src="assets/bit_blaster.png")

